People will tell you anything to acquire whatever they need- love, sex, friendship, support, money, transportation, etc. Don't. Be. Used.
Relationships in general have similarities. So I have this with friendships and romantic relationships.
The reason being is because it is unhealthy. As much as I want to love people freely, it may return void.
I consider myself to be a very giving person. If I like someone, i really genuinely put my all. But I've had to stop that.
That doesn't mean to not let people in, but it is to be cautious.
The #1 thing I learned from my last relationship was to protect yourself. Guard yourself. Guard your heart.
People are anything.
